{"tid":953912,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"港男戰勝港女「霸位黨」　愛車事後疑被港女刮花！","createTime":"2018-12-24T09:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T15:02:51.000Z","uid":225464,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"386eab970b6dda4d0a6bc6d627d4b8fdd859e523","tid":953912,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/bkn-20181224163337012-1224_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181224%2Fbkn-20181224163337012-1224_00822_001.html&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0f03f11a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/bkn-20181224163337012-1224_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MVf1q5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MVf1q5.jpg&h=4689afca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>港男戰勝商場「霸位黨」　愛車事後疑遭殃？</strong><br />\n<br />\n假日停車位一向都比較搶手。惟最近有司機指在停車場尋找泊位，竟遇上有港女試圖「人肉霸車位」。雖然司機最終成功泊車，但事後卻發現愛車被人刮花。<br />\n<br />\n該司機的朋友將片段上載至Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」，畫面所見，上周六（22日）下午約2時20分，當時有車輛正準備駛離新城市中央廣場內的停車場泊位。一名頭戴粉紅色鴨舌帽的女子隨即急步上前，站於車位前方霸位。<br />\n<br />\n當時該司機正駕車停在附近等候，待女子稍一分神，站至一旁時，便趁機泊進停車位內。女子即時上前，並指︰「我等緊呢個位㗎喎，（架車）啱啱過緊嚟囉」。惟他未有理會，反指︰「你真係搞笑，你架車呢？已經擺喺度㗎」？<br />\n<br />\n原以為事件已告一段落，未料事後該司機發現，愛車被人刮出一條長長的花痕。他氣言︰「人預咗捉你唔到，不過我都報咗警！商場都會睇閉路電視」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民均不值女子霸車位的行為：「仲人肉霸位，醜唔醜呀」、「停車場都要霸？畀得你入一定有位喎」。又有人祝司機早日找到「刮車兇手」。"},{"pid":"e27220ad2fce506f3a95b8dd287608c4264333b2","tid":953912,"uid":159176,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"班香港人真係好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfb8362f9692f0ab54a4ad5dbb9fb1ae5ec1320","tid":953912,"uid":126648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"正坫<br />\n垃圾 之前外國有單又係女人霸車位"},{"pid":"c15fd8242767d047fb38d159da0e4fbc6236d91e","tid":953912,"uid":111872,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"人肉霸位真係好撚乞衣"},{"pid":"1d42864f8b3057049fcf0a806c675be5cc6dbd42","tid":953912,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"又同支那表軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95a61f10fdb7ef3d193eb6bd66763de5704c172","tid":953912,"uid":76822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b574fcafba12b7ad40dc90a281515b33f47f51e","tid":953912,"uid":170297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AlltimeGreatestClipsShow/videos/1680628875349731/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAlltimeGreatestClipsShow%2Fvideos%2F1680628875349731%2F&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0698611d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AlltimeGreatestClipsShow/videos/1680628875349731/</a> 之前有個女人柒到出外國"},{"pid":"56e920dc1ff2b83fa811ebccd17bef37d370599c","tid":953912,"uid":119778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b574fcafba12b7ad40dc90a281515b33f47f51e","tid":953912,"uid":170297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AlltimeGreatestClipsShow/videos/1680628875349731/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAlltimeGreatestClipsShow%2Fvideos%2F1680628875349731%2F&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0698611d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AlltimeGreatestClipsShow/videos/1680628875349731/</a> 之前有個女人柒到出外國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"個司機最後都係讓 on9"},{"pid":"853dfb62569623fdb58821e8b8de3a5b4ae92141","tid":953912,"uid":75072,"like":1,